  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  all children aged 6 months to 5 years admitted to SFC outpatient care during the study
             period

          -  WHM between 70-79% (1977 NCHS/WHO standard) without edema

          -  approval from the caretaker

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  presence of the following signs: bilateral edema, MUAC&lt;110 mm , WHM&lt; 70%(criteria for
             severe malnutrition), and medical complications necessitating hospitalisation

          -  refusal to participate from caretaker
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
